  "detailed_description": "Koi Farm is a game about playing with koi ponds. Explore an infinite number of procedurally generated koi patterns by crossbreeding your fish, and discover new mutations as you go along.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br>Create beautiful koi through selective breeding, and combine fish with interesting patterns and colors to refine them.<br><br>Store the best koi as collectible trading cards, and let the koi book guide you towards new undiscovered mutations.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1518810/extras/96f0824aa10a244d97e76d5f6d8067fe.avif?t=1770063631\" width=572 height=262 /></span><br><br>Generate <i>koi codes</i>, which can be shared with other players and dropped into their games to spawn the koi.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1518810/extras/e57910a21b20a506d534df5d7df23dd5.avif?t=1770063631\" width=256 height=256 /></span>",
